data.description: Welcome home to this 4-bed, 2-bath gem! Enjoy the spacious open concept with a split bedroom floor-plan, ideal for modern living. With tile in all trafficked areas, new interior paint, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances, this beauty is move-in ready. The pebble tec pool, dog run for your furry friends, and the privacy of no rear neighbors make it a true paradise. Located in the sought-after Vail School District, this is the perfect place to call home.
